## Essential Context

- `window.__domRacerDebug` must not exist in source/build.
- Centralized tuning: `gameConfig.ts` groups (TIMING, TOAST, COINS, SPECIALS, EFFECTS, JACKPOT, POLICE, PLANE, ENCOUNTER, OVERGROWTH, NEAR_MISS, OBJECTIVES, PLAYER, VEHICLES).
- Runtime modules are pure functions: logic in `*Runtime.ts`, orchestration in `Game.ts`.
- Sprite files in `src/game/sprites/`; consumers import from barrel `./sprites`.
- ESLint + Prettier. Scripts: `lint`, `lint:fix`, `format`, `format:check`.
- 81 smoke tests across 8 files. `npm run test` / `npm run build` must pass.
- Police chase lifecycle in `encounterRuntime.ts` ŌĆö base duration 4000-6000ms, escalates with run time.
- Overgrowth: `OvergrowthStage = 'grass' | 'bush' | 'tree'`. Config: `GROWTH_GRASS_TO_BUSH_MS`, `GROWTH_BUSH_TO_TREE_MS`. Anchors from obstacles + slowZones.
- Special pickup shapes: helpful (bonus/magnet/ghost/invert) = rounded square + chevron, harmful (blur/oil_slick/reverse) = diamond, mystery = circle, jackpot = star.
- Form controls (input/textarea/select/radio/checkbox) scanned as `wall` ŌåÆ `slowZones`.
- All score increments multiples of 10. Near-miss is visual-only (no score).
- Extension popup: static HTML in `public/popup.html`. No JS build step.
- Adaptive sprite contrast: `applyAdaptiveShadow()`/`clearAdaptiveShadow()` in `spriteHelpers.ts`.
- Branding: pixel-art SVG wordmark in `branding/`, PNGs generated via `generate_assets.py` using `rsvg-convert`.
- Game toggle: Shift+Space (or Shift+Backtick). Popup "Start Game" button also toggles.
- Scrollbar: only `<body>` gets `overflow: hidden`. Wheel/touchmove listeners prevent scrolling.
- Unsupported page detection: sad screen when too few elements to race on.

## Constraints To Preserve

- No screen shake
- Playful, readable, non-violent tone
- Keep controls/core loop stable
- Only specials expire over time, not regular coins
- Game settings (sound, vehicle) are global, not per-tab
